Dependencies:

kdelibs         (required)
cdrtools        (required)
cdparanoia      (required)
cdrdao          (recommended)
taglib          (recommended)
flac            (recommended)
lame            (recommended)
normalize       (recommended)
libsndfile      (recommended)
dvd+rw-tools    (optional)
libsamplerate   (optional)

ffmpeg          (optional)
 * decodes WMA and others

musicbrainz     (optional)
 * fills in tags by matching current song with an online database of song
   "fingerprints".  This can be useful when creating so called "CD-Text"
   enabled Cds.
